title: 난 안 예쁘고 키도 작고 뚱뚱해🥺💔: JESSIA - I'm Not Pretty (2021) [가사해석/번역]
description:
🔥🔥🔥
미디어가 그려내는 외모에 나를 맞추면 돌아오는 건 병이랍니다



[Chorus]
Maybe I'm not pretty
나 안 예쁜 것 같아
Maybe I'm just fun
그냥 작고 통통하기만 해
(* Funsized = 키가 작고 귀여운)
'Cause I got a belly and I got a bum
배도 좀 나왔고 엉덩이도 크니까
And I'm f**king jelly of all the other ones
다른 애들이 진심 너무 부러워
With their itty bitty bellies and their rump-ump-ump-ums
걔넨 배도 안 나왔고 엉덩이도 조막만하니까

[Verse 1]
I know that I should love myself
나를 사랑하라는 건 알겠는데
But it's getting kinda hard when you're constantly feeling like garbage
계속 쓰레기처럼 느껴지는데 어떻게 그래?
Know I shouldn't hurt myself
이게 자해란 건 알고는 있는데,
But I can't find a way to lose weight without literally starving
대체 굶는 거 말고 살은 어떻게 빼는 건데?

[Pre-Chorus]
Every other song says I'm beautiful
다른 노래 가사에서는 그래, 난 예쁘대
But what if I don't feel like I'm beautiful?
그런데 내 눈엔 내가 안 예쁜데 어떡해?
I wish my body image didn't say
제발 내 머릿속에서 그만 말하라 그래
That I should be another kinda way
내 몸매는 이렇게 생기면 안 된다고 좀 그만 해

[Chorus]
Maybe I'm not pretty
나 안 예쁜 것 같아
Maybe I'm just fun
그냥 작고 통통하기만 해
'Cause I got a belly and I got a bum
배도 나왔고 엉덩이도 좀 크니까
But I can't be jelly of all the other ones
그렇다고 다른 애들을 질투하면 되겠어?
So I'm falling in lovе with my rump-ump-ump-um
그러니까 내가 이 엉덩이 사랑해줄래

[Verse 2]
I'm not gonna ask for help
나 이제 고민 말 안 할래
'Cause all you're gonna say is
어차피 다들 이럴텐데, 내가 왜
"You'rе perfect and oh, you're so worth it"
"넌 그대로 완벽해, 정말 소중해"
But sometimes I hate myself
나 가끔은 내가 너무 싫은데
I get inside my head and I think that I somehow deserve this
생각하다 보면 그럴 만 하다고 착각까지 해

[Pre-Chorus]
Every other song says I'm beautiful
다른 노래 가사 들으면 난 예쁘대

About Anne-Marie:
Anne-Marie has proved to be one of the UK’s most exciting and successful British breakthrough popstars of recent years. A former 3x world karate champion and West End child star-turned 9x BRIT Award nominee, A-M’s rise has been nothing short of meteoric. In 2018 Anne-Marie released her debut album, ‘Speak Your Mind’ which featured the hit singles 'Alarm', 'Ciao Adios', 'Heavy', 'Friends', '2002' and 'Perfect to Me'. She subsequently ended that year as as the UK’s biggest-selling debut artist, selling out headline shows and playing stadium dates supporting long-time friend and champion Ed Sheeran in the process.

She has also sang on and co-written many other hits such as Birthday, Rockabye, Don't Leave Me Alone,  To Be Young, f*ck, i'm lonely and Don't Play, collaborating with the likes of Clean Bandit, Marshmello, David Guetta, Lauv, Rudimental, Doja Cat and KSI, as well as starring on The Greatest Showman: Reimagined soundtrack performing Rewrite the stars alongside James Arthur.
